<subSubSection pageId="237" pageNumber="842" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="237.[171,1378,291,1070]" pageId="237" pageNumber="842">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[173,522,883,912]" pageId="237" pageNumber="842">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Near Threatened on The IUCN Red List. Taliabu [sland is damaged by human activities such as logging, and recent fires have damaged the only remaining patch of primary forest, which might negatively affect the poorly known Sula Archipelago Rat.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
